            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="grc">
                <lg met="Dodecasyllable">
               <l><lb n="1"/><g ref="#cross">+</g><choice><orig>Ί</orig><reg>Ἵ</reg></choice>ππων ἀκεστὴρ εὐσεβὴς Νικηφόρος·</l><l>θερμῶ κινηθεὶς <lb n="2"/>ἐνδιαθέτω πόθω·</l><l>ἀνιστόρησεν ἐμφερῶς τὴν εἰκόνα:</l><l><lb n="3"/>τοῦ παμμεγίστου μάρτυρος Γεωργίου:</l><l>κἀν τῆδε σεπτῶς τῆ μονῆ τῶν <lb n="4"/>φορβίω<expan><ex>ν</ex></expan></l> <l>ποθῶν ἐφευρεῖν ἀντίληψιν <choice><orig>ε</orig><reg>ἐ</reg></choice>ν κρίσει:</l><l>τ<choice><orig>ὼ</orig><reg>ῶ</reg></choice> ὑπεραυγῆ <lb n="5"/>μάρτυρα στε<unclear>φ</unclear>ανίτη<unclear>ν</unclear></l><l><expan><abbr>κ</abbr><ex>αὶ</ex></expan> τ<supplied reason="lost">ὰ</supplied>ς προσευχ<expan><ex>ὰς</ex></expan> τῶν μενόντων <lb n="6"/>ἐνθάδε:-</l></lg> 
                <lb n="7"/><w lemma="δέησις"><expan><abbr rend="supraline">Δέ</abbr><ex>ησις</ex></expan></w> Νικηφό <lb n="8" break="no"/>ρου τοῦ Καλληά
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <p>PENDING</p>
                 </div>
            <div type="translation"> 
                <p>A healer of horses, Nikephoros the pious,
                moved by warm heartfelt desire with like feeling painted the image 
                of the very great martyr George;
                amd revently in this monastery of the Phorbia,
                desirous of finding help at [the] Judjement from the most brilliant crowned martyr, and the prayers of those dwelling here.
                Invocation of Nikephoros the farrier (?)</p> 
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Good condition. A cross marks the beginning and the end of the text.</p>
            </div>
